  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Bariatric surgery may attenuate insulin resistance and low-grade inflammation in obese
      subjects. This trial aims to test whether exercise training can add to the benefits of
      bariatric surgery on insulin sensitivity and inflammation. In addition, this study aims to
      investigate whether exercise training can counteract bone loss induced by bariatric surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
